921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T08:58:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"153e0f88e81d9e0f3a3b992ba35f4b9811b3a1ed","tid":2204660,"uid":103965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T08:59:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d1f55cb1457bbc47e6df4c14afd3d8eb6097b5a","tid":2204660,"uid":198175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T09:02:03.000Z","msg":"點止認罪, 遲吓仲會拍片上埋電視玩讀稿認罪, 支共大把嘢可以玩"},{"pid":"1132d8020af1111cd8f4836d9fbc0a98079ad5a7","tid":2204660,"uid":57675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T09:02:15.000Z","msg":"律師會會長彭韻僖回應說，希望在大陸法下，當局可用更高透明度處理涉案人士被捕及扣押，做法會更可取。<br />\n連呢條垃圾都咁樣講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85a0fe035b564eb2a448f82ca2b33030a708dbb6","tid":2204660,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d1f55cb1457bbc47e6df4c14afd3d8eb6097b5a","tid":2204660,"uid":198175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T09:02:03.000Z","msg":"點止認罪, 遲吓仲會拍片上埋電視玩讀稿認罪, 支共大把嘢可以玩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T09:05:37.000Z","msg":"新彊人:  我思想有問題所以先會被送去再教育營,  感謝政府....<br />\n<br />\n要搞到你認錯好易,  你唔肯認事後私刑玩殘你"},{"pid":"0e8f1f6ff4161e8f5b31fa0bb8e26608da1fe672","tid":2204660,"uid":171484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb8ae03ac68ac2929fd358039abdbc5a1ae6374b","tid":2204660,"uid":14918,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T08:28:23.000Z","msg":"呢個澳門人咁有風骨ge<br />\n<br />\n綁架華年達案發生於2001年2月28日，是自澳門特別行政區成立後首次有大律師被綁架的案件。案中綁匪在澳門西灣擄走正在駕車途中的澳門資深大律師華年達，並將其收藏在馬交石山一座高層大廈的單位內，且對其進行虐待。<br />\n<br />\n被綁架的人質為澳門資深大律師華年達，生於葡萄牙里斯本，曾擔任澳門律師公會主席、澳門立法會議員等職務[參 5]，也在澳門為葡萄牙社會黨創辦分支組織；故在澳門和葡萄牙也頗有名氣[參 6]。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T09:11:12.000Z","msg":"呢條友經常彈出彈入<br />\n咪撚信<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bZbxSTc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbZbxSTc.png&h=d5346d5d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a22d7b0451cca55333a6823862267f58ea39c5a5","tid":2204660,"uid":346260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T15:03:08.000Z","msg":"大家唔該簽署同喺 Facebook, Twitter, tg, whatsapp 等等廣傳呢個 petition：<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-chinese-officials-culpable-wrongfully-detaining-12-hong-kong-citizens-and-denying-their-right-counsel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsanction-chinese-officials-culpable-wrongfully-detaining-12-hong-kong-citizens-and-denying-their-right-counsel&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTvcg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=badcd270\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-chinese-officials-culpable-wrongfully-detaining-12-hong-kong-citizens-and-denying-their-right-counsel</a><br />\n如果呢個 petition 喺2020年10月12日之前收集咗100,000個簽署,白宮就必須對此作出回應。呢個 petition 請求特朗普團隊去制裁嗰啲拘捕,扣留同剝奪十二名香港人法律權利嘅中國官員同其他相關人士。咁會對十二名香港人嘅處境有莫大嘅幫助，所以懇請大家提供協助。謝謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n=====================<br />\n大家要注意資安，尤其是被咬過嘅手足，電話可能已經被入侵。港共可以用stingray大規模監控某個大範圍嘅所有電話，偷取IMSI，可以識別您，甚至截取通訊。好多手足就係唔注重資安被咬，好大機會包括被綁架12人; 記得追蹤基爾巴 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/96327\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/96327</a><br />\n<br />\n[/orange][/u][/b][/size=1][實用文] 教您點先可以保障私隱、網絡安全 (簡易版)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2194107\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2194107</a><br />\n樓主可唔可以pin?"}]}